<h2 style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 22px; color: #111827;">You've been invited!</h2>

<p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #374151;">
    <strong>{{inviterName}}</strong> has invited you to join <strong>{{orgName}}</strong> on Zenith.
</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #374151;">
    Click the button below to accept the invitation and get started:
</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
    {{> button url=inviteLink label="Accept Invitation"}}
</div>

<p style="margin: 24px 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">
    Or copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
    <a href="{{{inviteLink}}}" style="color: #2563eb; word-break: break-all;">{{inviteLinkDisplay}}</a>
</p>